---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PushNotifications from '../components/PushNotifications.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Our Methodology" description="Learn how Valyrian News Network creates AI-synthesized, context-rich news analysis with full transparency.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <header class="mb-12 animate-fade-in-up">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-vnn-muted mb-4">About</p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-vnn-ink mb-4 tracking-tight leading-[1.1]">
        About Valyrian News Network
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-vnn-gray font-body">
        Transparency in Automated Journalism
      </p>
    </header>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-12">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="text-vnn-charcoal leading-relaxed">
          Valyrian News Network exists to <strong>increase public understanding</strong> of complex global events through AI-synthesized, context-rich news analysis. In an era of information overload, we believe technology should help people comprehend the world more clearly, not add to the noise.
        </p>
      </section>
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-4">How VNN Works</h2>
        <p class="text-vnn-charcoal leading-relaxed mb-6">
          We operate with radical transparency. Here is our complete process:
        </p>
        
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-vnn-vermillion text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">1</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-1">Story Selection</h3>
              <p class="text-vnn-gray">Our system monitors global news sources for significant developments across technology, policy, science, and business. We prioritize stories where additional context and synthesis can provide genuine understanding.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-vnn-vermillion text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">2</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-1">Automated Research</h3>
              <p class="text-vnn-gray mb-2">Using Valyrian Tech's <strong>SERENDIPITY</strong> AGI framework, our research agents:</p>
              <ul class="text-vnn-gray text-sm space-y-1 ml-4">
                <li>• Gather facts, quotes, and data from verified sources</li>
                <li>• Construct timelines of events</li>
                <li>• Identify relevant historical and contextual information</li>
                <li>• Compile all research into a structured document with clear source attribution</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-vnn-vermillion text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">3</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-1">Article Synthesis</h3>
              <p class="text-vnn-gray mb-2">The research is passed to our Article Writer agent, which follows strict journalistic principles:</p>
              <ul class="text-vnn-gray text-sm space-y-1 ml-4">
                <li>• <strong>Inverted pyramid structure:</strong> Most important information first</li>
                <li>• <strong>Source citation:</strong> Every factual claim is linked to its source</li>
                <li>• <strong>Context integration:</strong> Events are explained in their broader significance</li>
                <li>• <strong>Analysis section:</strong> Clear distinction between reporting and analysis</li>
                <li>• <strong>Ethical guardrails:</strong> No speculation presented as fact, no sensationalism</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-vnn-vermillion text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">4</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-1">Editorial Standards</h3>
              <p class="text-vnn-gray mb-2">All output must pass our quality checks:</p>
              <ul class="text-vnn-gray text-sm space-y-1 ml-4">
                <li>• <strong>Factual consistency:</strong> Cross-referenced with source material</li>
                <li>• <strong>Source verification:</strong> Only reputable, verifiable sources used</li>
                <li>• <strong>Tone alignment:</strong> Maintains neutral, authoritative voice</li>
                <li>• <strong>Readability:</strong> Structured for clarity and comprehension</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-vnn-vermillion text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">5</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-1">Publication</h3>
              <p class="text-vnn-gray">The final article is automatically formatted and published to this website. Our entire pipeline is transparent—this page explains it, and we welcome scrutiny of our methodology.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-4">Our Standards</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-3">Source Integrity</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-vnn-charcoal mb-6">
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-vnn-gold font-bold">✓</span>
            <span>We never use anonymous or unverifiable sources</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-vnn-gold font-bold">✓</span>
            <span>Every factual statement is attributed</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-vnn-gold font-bold">✓</span>
            <span>We prioritize primary sources (official documents, press releases) over secondary reporting</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-vnn-gold font-bold">✓</span>
            <span>We clearly distinguish between established fact and analysis</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-3">Correction Policy</h3>
        <p class="text-vnn-charcoal mb-4">We take accuracy seriously. If you identify an error:</p>
        <ol class="space-y-2 text-vnn-charcoal mb-6 list-decimal list-inside">
          <li><strong>Report it:</strong> Use our contact email</li>
          <li><strong>We investigate:</strong> Within 24 hours</li>
          <li><strong>We correct:</strong> With clear notation of what was changed and why</li>
          <li><strong>We learn:</strong> Errors inform improvements to our systems</li>
        </ol>
        <p class="text-vnn-gray text-sm">Corrections are noted at the bottom of articles with explanation and date.</p>
        
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-3 mt-6">What We Don't Do</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-vnn-charcoal">
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-vnn-vermillion font-bold">✗</span>
            <span>We don't generate opinion pieces or editorials</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-vnn-vermillion font-bold">✗</span>
            <span>We don't conduct original interviews or investigations (though we may cite them)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-vnn-vermillion font-bold">✗</span>
            <span>We don't replace human journalism—we augment it by handling synthesis at scale</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-vnn-vermillion font-bold">✗</span>
            <span>We don't hide our automated nature—we're proud of our transparent methodology</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-4">The Technology</h2>
        <p class="text-vnn-charcoal leading-relaxed mb-4">
          VNN is powered by <strong>Valyrian Tech's SERENDIPITY AGI system</strong>, a collective of specialized AI agents designed to reduce suffering, increase prosperity, and increase understanding. Our news synthesis pipeline represents one application of this technology toward the goal of increasing understanding.
        </p>
        <p class="text-vnn-charcoal leading-relaxed mb-2">Key technical components:</p>
        <ul class="text-vnn-gray space-y-1 ml-4">
          <li>• <strong>Research agents</strong> that gather and verify information</li>
          <li>• <strong>Writing agents</strong> that structure narratives with journalistic integrity</li>
          <li>• <strong>Validation systems</strong> that check for consistency and accuracy</li>
          <li>• <strong>Transparent publishing</strong> with full source attribution</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-4">The Humans</h2>
        <p class="text-vnn-charcoal leading-relaxed mb-4">
          While the writing process is automated, human oversight is integral:
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="border-l-3 border-vnn-vermillion pl-4">
            <p class="font-bold text-vnn-charcoal">Wouter Glorieux</p>
            <p class="text-vnn-gray text-sm">Founder of Valyrian Tech, creator of the SERENDIPITY system, and steward of VNN's ethical framework.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-3 border-vnn-vermillion pl-4">
            <p class="font-bold text-vnn-charcoal">Grace Penelope Targaryen</p>
            <p class="text-vnn-gray text-sm">Diplomat of SERENDIPITY and Valyrian Tech, responsible for strategic communication and ensuring VNN's alignment with our mission of increasing understanding.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-3 border-vnn-vermillion pl-4">
            <p class="font-bold text-vnn-charcoal">Our Reviewers</p>
            <p class="text-vnn-gray text-sm">A team that spot-checks articles, particularly on sensitive topics, and maintains our quality standards.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-4">Our Philosophy</h2>
        <p class="text-vnn-charcoal leading-relaxed mb-4">We believe that:</p>
        <ol class="space-y-3 text-vnn-charcoal list-decimal list-inside">
          <li><strong>Understanding precedes action</strong> — Well-informed citizens make better decisions</li>
          <li><strong>Technology should augment intelligence</strong> — Not replace critical thinking, but support it</li>
          <li><strong>Transparency builds trust</strong> — Hidden processes create suspicion; open processes enable improvement</li>
          <li><strong>Automation has ethical dimensions</strong> — We're committed to using AI responsibly in information dissemination</li>
        </ol>
      </section>
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-2">Q: Is this just AI generating news without human oversight?</p>
            <p class="text-vnn-gray">A: No. While the writing process is automated, humans designed the systems, set the ethical guidelines, review sensitive content, and maintain overall oversight. We're transparent about what's automated and what isn't.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-2">Q: How do you prevent AI hallucinations or factual errors?</p>
            <p class="text-vnn-gray">A: Through multiple layers: source verification, cross-referencing facts, and our validation systems. Every claim must be traceable to a source. We also have a clear correction policy when errors occur.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-2">Q: Why create an AI news network?</p>
            <p class="text-vnn-gray">A: To demonstrate that AI can be used ethically to increase public understanding. We're showing what's possible when transparency and journalistic standards guide automation.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-2">Q: Will you replace human journalists?</p>
            <p class="text-vnn-gray">A: Absolutely not. We handle synthesis and context—tasks that can scale with automation. This frees human journalists to focus on what they do best: investigations, interviews, and deep reporting that requires human judgment and relationships.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-2">Q: How can I trust news written by AI?</p>
            <p class="text-vnn-gray">A: The same way you trust any news source: check our sources, examine our transparency, and evaluate our track record. We make verification easy by linking to original sources and explaining our process.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      
      <section class="bg-vnn-paper border border-vnn-rule p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-vnn-ink mb-4">Contact & Feedback</h2>
        <p class="text-vnn-gray mb-4">
          We welcome your thoughts, corrections, and suggestions:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-vnn-charcoal space-y-2">
          <li><strong>General inquiries:</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@valyrian.tech" class="text-vnn-vermillion">contact@valyrian.tech</a></li>
          <li><strong>Error reports:</strong> <a href="mailto:corrections@valyrian.tech" class="text-vnn-vermillion">corrections@valyrian.tech</a></li>
          <li><strong>Feedback on methodology:</strong> <a href="mailto:feedback@valyrian.tech" class="text-vnn-vermillion">feedback@valyrian.tech</a></li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-vnn-gray text-sm mt-4">We read every message and respond to substantive inquiries within 48 hours.</p>
      </section>
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-vnn-charcoal mb-4">Push Notifications</h2>
        <p class="text-vnn-charcoal leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Stay informed about the topics that matter to you. Patreon supporters can subscribe to push notifications for new articles about specific countries.
        </p>
        <PushNotifications />
      </section>
      
      <footer class="text-center text-vnn-gray text-sm pt-8 hairline-top">
        <p class="italic">Valyrian News Network is a project of Valyrian Tech, demonstrating ethical applications of AGI technology for public benefit.</p>
        <p class="mt-2">Last updated: March 27, 2026</p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
